<span style="font-family: 宋体;">（一）</span> 不断提升服务质量，把外卖准时、安全、齐全送达消费者手中。</span></span><br /><span style="font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（二）</span> 文明礼貌，绝不讽刺、辱骂、殴打他人，树立良好职业形象。</span></span><br /><span style="font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（三）</span> 遵守交规，安全行驶，文明驾驶，绝不酒驾、醉驾。</span></span><br /><span style="font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（四）</span> 绝不泄露消费者或者合作商家的个人信息。</span></span><br /><span style="font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（五）</span> 绝不私自查看、品尝、损坏、</span><span style="line-height: 150%;">偷盗</span><span style="line-height: 150%;">消费者所购产品。</span></span><br /><span style="font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（六）</span> 用文明规范的服务传递正能量，并且不传谣、不信谣。</span></span><br /><span style="font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（七）</span> 绝不从事抢劫、伤害、盗窃等</span><span style="line-height: 150%;">违法</span><span style="line-height: 150%;">行为。</span></span><br /><span style="font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">（八）</span> 绝不参与制毒、贩毒、吸毒、嫖娼等法律严厉禁止的危害自身、影响职业形象的行为。</span></span><br /><br /><span style="font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">第五条</span> 骑手应保证自身身体条件可胜任骑行工作，未患有不宜骑行的身体疾病。如有不适，应立即告知公司。</span></span><br /><br /><span style="font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">第六条</span> 骑手应严格遵守公司制定的《骑手电动车使用约定》，并承诺：</span></span><br /><span style="font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 150%;">（一）要爱护车辆，保持车辆干净，并定期对车辆进行维护和保养。</span></span><br /><span style="font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 150%;">（二）在骑行期间，应严格遵守交通规则，安全驾驶，文明驾驶，在法律准许的车道驾驶，不酒后、药后驾驶，不疲劳驾驶，不超速驾驶，不危险驾驶（如闯红灯、抢道、飙车、逆行等），不在出现坍塌、积水、坑槽等危险路段驾驶。</span></span><br /><span style="font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 150%;">（三）在通过人行横道时，应避让行人，与行人保持安全距离。</span></span><br /><span style="font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 150%;">（四）在骑行期间不得接听电话，若接听电话，应就近寻找安全</span><span style="line-height: 150%;">、</span><span style="line-height: 150%;">可停靠地点，停车后再接听、拨打电话。</span></span><br /><span style="font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 150%;">（五）在配送过程中，不得在车辆上搭载其他物品，不得载人行驶。</span></span><br /><span style="font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 150%;">（六）工作期间必须身着美团外卖专用工服，并且保证在骑行期间佩戴安全帽，做好安全保护措施。</span></span><br /><br /><span style="font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', \'PingFang SC\', sans-serif; font-size: 12px;"><span style="line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">第七条</span> 驾驶车辆发生交通事故，应</span><span style="line-height: 150%;">在